Create HTML file in webapp folder.
Create HTML form with 2 input box email & password.
Create HTTP Servlet class as LoginServlet.
Override doPost method.
Send request from html file to servlet class.
Fetch email & password in servlet class.
Write a jdbc code to verify email & password in db application.
Print output on browser whether email & password is valid or invalid.
If credentials are valid - display Home.html - Login Successful!!
If credentials are invalid - display Login.html - Invalid credentials